    <h2>Common Customer Service Queries</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Flight Changes and Cancellations:</strong> Adjust or cancel bookings quickly via a live agent.</li>
        <li><strong>Hotel Booking Issues:</strong> Fix issues such as incorrect dates or missing reservations.</li>
        <li><strong>Refunds and Compensation:</strong> Claim refunds or compensation for disruptions.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Summary of Lufthansa Contact Options</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Phone Support (☎1-888-829-1117):</strong> Available 24/7 for urgent issues.</li>
        <li><strong>Live Chat:</strong> Accessible via the Lufthansa website’s Help section.</li>
        <li><strong>Social Media:</strong> Message Lufthansa on Twitter or Facebook.</li>
        <li><strong>Mobile App:</strong> Chat or call support directly from the app.</li>
        <li><strong>Email Support:</strong> Ideal for non-urgent matters requiring documentation.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Tips for Faster Help</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Have your booking details or itinerary ready.</li>
